snippet.title: Amber Heard Is Trying To Avoid Jail After Having A Baby!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Is Trying To Avoid Jail After Having A Baby!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell to never miss out on your daily dose of Celeb Tea!

Welcome Back To Our Channel,  In This Video we will talk about How Amber Heard is trying to avoid jail By having a baby.

Amber Heard has a baby! The 35 year old actress is celebrating the birth of a baby girl, only months after her ex-husband, Johnny Depp, lost a libel case involving her.

Amber Heard's lovely newborn girl, Oonagh, has been introduced to the world. She announced the news on Instagram in a lengthy post that discussed the nitty-gritty facts as well as the difficulties of femininity in general. In the said Instagram post’s caption, she wrote, "I’m so excited to share this news with you. Four years ago, I decided I wanted to have a child. I wanted to do it on my own terms. I now appreciate how radical it is for us as women to think about one of the most fundamental parts of our destinies in this way.
